* Somerville, Robert, &quot;The Council of Clermont (1095), and Latin Christian Society&quot;, &quot;Archivum Historiae Pontificiae&quot; 12 (1974): 55–90 
* Strack, Georg, &quot;The sermon of Urban II in Clermont 1095 and the Tradition of Papal Oratory&quot;, &quot;Medieval Sermon Studies&quot; 56 (2012): 30–45, (pdf).


